Dataset name: Etat du trafic en temps réel
Dataset brief description: Real-time traffic status. Data provided to Rennes Métropole by the company Autoroutes Trafic.** This data has a **3-minute delay**, so it is normal that at 3:30 PM, the most recent data indicates 3:27 PM. This dataset has been linked to a **specific layer of the RVA** to facilitate reuse.
